{"tid":515090,"cid":9,"subCid":0,"title":"［I/A］龍珠z 爆裂對戰 （59）","createTime":"2017-12-31T06:46:27.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-31T06:46:27.000Z","uid":56627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"864d099d9efeae108b3932e4a67af42906c24e19","tid":515090,"uid":56627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-31T06:46:27.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">鍾意用台/陸譯名既唔該過主</span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/5ctlse2k\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F5ctlse2k&h=0f7fb24d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: small;\">Credit 連狗巴打</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">活動</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/ju7205g4\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fju7205g4&h=73ca8c6a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/p73v24bc\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fp73v24bc&h=971e2044&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/wl6j1vrf\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fwl6j1vrf&h=ba14ff19&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">卡池</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/81bmd574\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F81bmd574&h=9f03a869&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n〜 2017/12/27 15:59 (香港時間)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/dpxaj45l\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fdpxaj45l&h=1d848a61&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n〜 2018/1/9 22:59 (香港時間)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/o5b0h8a6\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fo5b0h8a6&h=6f2aade9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n〜 2018/1/9 22:59 (香港時間)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">Q&amp;A</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\nQ. 綠石秘寶打邊關多？<br />\n<br />\nA. 24-7<br />\n<br />\n---<br />\n<br />\nQ. 潛解行邊條路先？<br />\n<br />\nA. 會10技既右下，唔會既左上 (右下&gt;左上&gt;右上&gt;左下)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">新手教學</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: small;\">感謝 冥幣巴整合</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n其實你想知咩新手資料???大部分巴哈都有<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n1. 每日我建議新手打龜仙人、Satan武道會、雲上活動，之後去攞獎品<br />\n<br />\n2. 如果係升Rank嘅，<del>我估大家現在都係以力隊為主</del>，請趁現在3倍經驗解主線<del>Easy解到21-1(目覚めたさきに)</del>，之後再解到<del>呢關</del>最高難度，<del>力隊超4悟打體波易到爆</del>，順便刷綠石(打蘭芝同畢拉夫)換下新手角<br />\n<br />\n3. 如果係打覺醒料，可以去覺醒活動關打<br />\n<br />\n4. 升到D卡咁上下，請先去解超本氣果關，每日打潛力解放材料<br />\n<br />\n(開放條件:<br />\n<br />\nA. Rank 50以上<br />\n<br />\nB.「超本気の超決戦」ステージ2.激突！超サイヤ人孫悟空のZ-HARD Clear)<br />\n<br />\n5. 三倍經驗完左可以去刷每日強襲角，知、速角優先，刷的意思係講每隻刷10隻刷到10技，再刷多隻5技放倉，準備以後解超強襲.<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">角色代號</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: small;\">感謝 格劍巴整合代號名單</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/8of6x7b3\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F8of6x7b3&h=edec8fbd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: small;\">舊代號名單 感謝 photomore 巴打整合</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/02/19/031403_0f8104b2440ce5433f5504d1e13acd65.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F02%2F19%2F031403_0f8104b2440ce5433f5504d1e13acd65.jpg&d=6egmeV7Uw4Hi0nDUAOnDBC7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=889cea00\" target=\"_blank\">https://img.eservice-hk.net